On September 29th at the 2022 SSRL/LCLS Users Meeting, I was awarded the [Ferrel Lytle Award](https://www-ssrl.slac.stanford.edu/content/ssrl-news/farrel-w-lytle-award) for my service as Chair of the Users Executive Committee during the threat to shutdown SSRL in 2017.
The award usually goes to SSRL employees.
There are many excellent current employees who definitely merit winning it.
